<h4><a href="http://stdaily.com/index/kejixinwen/2020-12/08/content_1058267.shtml">迄今最轻薄有机发光二极管面世</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1385029" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/523ca84ef3b8443fad6067333a01d4c2.jpg" alt="" width="460" height="300" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/523ca84ef3b8443fad6067333a01d4c2.jpg 460w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/523ca84ef3b8443fad6067333a01d4c2-360x235.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px" /></p>
<p>物理学家组织网消息，英国科学家在《自然・通信》杂志上撰文指出，他们借助新方法，研制出了迄今最耐用、最轻、最薄的光源。这种新型有机发光二极管（LED）有望对未来手机和平板电脑的设计产生重大影响，让这些设备的显示器可折叠起来，同时也有望促进脑科学的发展。</p>
<p>研究人员指出，新光源不仅坚固耐用，而且极具力学柔韧性，未来除了可应用于移动技术领域之外，还可被整合到工作台表面、包装和衣物内，用于可穿戴设备，以及在生物医学研究中用作植入物。</p>
<h4><a href="https://view.inews.qq.com/a/20201208A0E1WZ00">华为发布首款商用台式机</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1385030" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/641.jpeg" alt="" width="641" height="427" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/641.jpeg 641w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/641-360x240.jpeg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 641px) 100vw, 641px" /></p>
<p>《一线》消息，华为昨天发布了其首款商用台式机 HUAWEI MateStation B515，这是华为继今年 8 月的 HUAWEI MateBook B 系列笔记本后在商用 PC 领域的又一重磅产品。</p>
<p>MateStation B515 搭载 AMD Ryzen 5 4600G 或 Ryzen 7 4700G 处理器，配备 8GB/16GB 双通道 DDR4-3200MHz 内存。显示器采用了一块 23.8 英寸的屏幕，屏占比达到 90%。机箱整体采用新中式格栅元素面板，8L 机身，比传统台式机机身节省 2/3 的空间。</p>
<h4>ThinkPad 史上最轻笔记本电脑 X1 Nano 发布</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1385031" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a8bf8214f4d21cb.jpg" alt="" width="1265" height="755" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a8bf8214f4d21cb.jpg 1265w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a8bf8214f4d21cb-360x215.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a8bf8214f4d21cb-768x458.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/a8bf8214f4d21cb-1024x611.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1265px) 100vw, 1265px" /></p>
<p>联想昨天正式发布 ThinkPad 史上最轻笔记本电脑 X1 Nano，其机身采用航空级碳纤维以及镁合金材质，重量为 907g。X1 Nano 搭载第 11 代智能英特尔酷睿处理器，采用 13 英寸 2k 分辨率高清屏幕，支持杜比视界，最高支持 450nits 亮度。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://36kr.com/newsflashes/1002051781170178">淘宝特价版将「1 元包邮」常态化</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1385032" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7662ff5716eb504f048c2afcf1975e20.jpg" alt="" width="1440" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7662ff5716eb504f048c2afcf1975e20.jpg 1440w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7662ff5716eb504f048c2afcf1975e20-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7662ff5716eb504f048c2afcf1975e20-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7662ff5716eb504f048c2afcf1975e20-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px" /></p>
<p>36kr 消息，淘宝特价版官方宣布将持续推进「1 元包邮」业务的常态化，确定每月最后一周为「1 元更香节」，超百万件工厂直供好货将 1 元包邮。</p>
<p>从国家知识产权局商标局中国商标网查询获悉，淘宝特价版提交了「1 元更香」商标注册申请。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1063381.htm">苹果 Fitness + 健身服务下周正式上线</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1385033" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/747627dd96697c6.jpg" alt="" width="980" height="616" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/747627dd96697c6.jpg 980w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/747627dd96697c6-360x226.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/747627dd96697c6-768x483.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px" /></p>
<p>MacX 消息，苹果宣布其健身订阅服务 Apple Fitness+ 将于 12 月 14 日正式上线。Apple Fitness+ 可以将 Apple TV、iPhone 或 iPad 上的健身视频与 Apple Watch 上的数据同步，让用户看到自己的心率、燃烧的卡路里等。</p>
<p>Apple Fitness+ 首批登陆的国家包括美国、英国、澳大利亚、加拿大、爱尔兰和新西兰。</p>
<h4><a href="http://www.techweb.com.cn/world/2020-12-08/2815379.shtml">诺基亚被任命领导欧盟资助 6G 项目</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1385034" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nokia-Ericsson-6G.jpg" alt="" width="1875" height="1125" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nokia-Ericsson-6G.jpg 1875w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nokia-Ericsson-6G-360x216.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nokia-Ericsson-6G-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nokia-Ericsson-6G-1024x614.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1875px) 100vw, 1875px" /></p>
<p>TechWeb 消息，欧盟正在开启规划研究 6G，电信设备厂商诺基亚，已被任命领导欧盟资助的 6G 研究项目 Hexa-X。</p>
<p>Hexa-X 是欧盟的旗舰 6G 研究项目，旨在将欧洲关键的行业利益相关者聚集到一起，带头推进 6G 的重要一步。项目将于明年 1 月 1 日正式启动，预计持续两年半。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/philippegorov/blanc-mask-face-the-outdoors-with-your-modern-day-armor?utm_source=kickbooster-direct&amp;utm_medium=kickbooster&amp;utm_content=link&amp;utm_campaign=18f15594">有人设计了款未来感十足的全面罩</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1385035" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/mask2.jpg" alt="" width="672" height="423" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/mask2.jpg 672w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/mask2-360x227.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px" /></p>
<p>美国设计公司 Blanc 在众筹平台上线了一款未来感十足的全面罩 Blanc，并已获得超过目标金额十倍的众筹额，预计将于 2021 年 3 月出货。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1385036" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/mask.jpg" alt="" width="593" height="424" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/mask.jpg 593w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/mask-360x257.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 593px) 100vw, 593px" /></p>
<p>设计采用复合人体工学的设计，佩戴者可从面罩的黑色条带部分看到面罩外的情况。安全保护方面，面罩搭载了两个通过 SGS 认证的可替换 HEPA 过滤器。Blanc 还将支持红、黄、粉等多种配色选择。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/12/thunderbolt-project-by-frgmt-pokemon-beijing-skp-s">Thunderbolt Project 推出 SKP-S 限量系列</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1385038" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/chain.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="708" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/chain.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/chain-360x212.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/chain-768x453.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/chain-1024x604.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息， fragment design 与 Pokémon 合作打造的 Thunderbolt Project By FRGMT &amp; Pokémon 系列将于 12 月 12 日至 2021 年 1 月 1 日在北京 SKP-S 开设限时店。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1385039" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/wer.jpg" alt="" width="1170" height="663" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/wer.jpg 1170w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/wer-360x204.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/wer-768x435.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/wer-1024x580.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1170px) 100vw, 1170px" /></p>
<p>除了原有的皮卡丘系列外，这次限时店还将为 SKP-S 店推出限量的可达鸭产品。整个系列包括毛绒玩具、靠枕、包袋、手机壳、T-Shirt、连帽卫衣和教练外套等单品，定价从 469 至 1499 元不等。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnet.com/news/black-mirror-creators-announce-death-to-2020-netflix-comedy-special/#ftag=CAD590a51e">《黑镜》创作者打造圣诞特辑《Death to 2020》</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1385040" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/f.jpg" alt="" width="1971" height="712" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/f.jpg 1971w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/f-360x130.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/f-768x277.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/f-1024x370.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1971px) 100vw, 1971px" /></p>
<p>Netflix 在官方 Twitter 公布，虽然今年没有《黑镜》更新，但《黑镜》创作者打造了另一个圣诞喜剧特辑《Death to 2020》，Samuel L. Jackson、Hugh Grant、Lisa Kudrow、Leslie Jones 等众多着名演员都将参演。</p>
<p>此前，Hugh Grant 在接受采访时曾提及该影片。当时，他表示这是一部基于 2020 年所发生事件的伪纪录片，自己在其中饰演一名历史学家。目前，Netflix 暂未公布影片上线日期。</p>
